.:: Zebra puzzle ::.
Color: red, green, ivory, yellow, blue
Food: banana, raspberry, cauliflower, grapefruit, lime
Cigar: old-gold, kools, chesterfields, lucky-strike, parliaments
Flower: poppy, sunflower, daffodil, balloon-flower, dahlia
Pet: dog, fox, zebra, horse, snails

1. Food:banana == Color:red
2. Food:raspberry == Pet:dog
3. Flower:poppy == Color:green
4. Food:cauliflower == Flower:sunflower
5. Color:green is to the right of Color:ivory
6. Cigar:old-gold == Pet:snails
7. Cigar:kools == Color:yellow
8. Flower:daffodil is in the middle
9. Food:grapefruit is on the far left
10. Cigar:chesterfields is on the left or right of Pet:fox
11. Cigar:kools is to the left or right of Pet:horse
12. Cigar:lucky-strike == Flower:balloon-flower
13. Food:lime == Cigar:parliaments
14. Food:grapefruit is to the left or right of Color:blue

.:: Answer ::.
|		|       1	|	2	|	3 	|	4	|	5	|
| Food	|   grapefruit	|    cauliflower	|     banana	|    raspberry	|    lime	|
| Color		|    yellow	|      blue	|      red	|     ivory	|     green	|
| Flower	|     dahlia	|      sunflower	|      daffodil	| balloon-flower	|     poppy	|
| Cigar		|     kools	| chesterfield	|    olg-gold	| lucky-strike	|   parliament	|
| Pet		|     fox	|     horse	|     snails	|     dog	|     zebra	|
